---
title: Thai-inspired Beef Stir-fry with bell pepper and peanuts
description: A sweet, salty and aromatic marinade coats the beef in this noodle dish. A scattering of peanuts at the end adds crunch and nuttiness for a meal that's easy to throw together but has a complex flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R16_W39_IE_IEQB26624-2_Main_high-a403807b.jpg
